Reasoning: 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is likely because the paper deals with discrete characters and their evolutionary scenarios. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely because the paper discusses the computational complexity of the counting and sampling problems for SCJ scenarios. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a possibility because the SCJ operation can be seen as a geometric operation on chromosomes. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possibility because the paper discusses the concept of most parsimonious SCJ scenarios, which can be seen as a game-theoretic optimization problem. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility because the paper proposes algorithms for computing SCJ scenarios and discusses their complexity.
